join Harlequin center
Harlequin: I see you've spoken to everyone now, little lamb.
if {Globals.colombina} == true:
	Harlequin: And I also see you chose the mask of Colombina.
	Harlequin: I wonder how much you know of her history, and of my mine...
	You: The Harlequin chuckles.
	Harlequin: Be that as it may. I choose to be flattered.
elif {Globals.dottore} == true:
	Harlequin: You chose the mask of the Doctor.
	Harlequin: I wonder if it served you well. Knowledge is seldom the high card you seek among these Lords and Ladies.
	Harlequin: But perhaps you were able to get through to some more reasonable ones.
	Harlequin: Just remember, we are here to burn it all to the ground.
	Harlequin: Don't get attached, as they're all complicit in the oppression of others like you.
elif {Globals.gnaga} == true:
	Harlequin: Did you feel particularly astute in the mask of the cat?
	Harlequin: Or perhaps you got lost in the details.
	Harlequin: Just remember, not everything is as it seems, and clues you would find proof in your world might not be in ours.
else:
	Harlequin: The mask of the Wolves themselves can be quite overpowering.
	Harlequin: I certainly hope you did not make enemies of our three candidates.
Harlequin: Perhaps you already think you know who [b]Roseus[/b] is.
Harlequin: This is where this demonstration ends, however.
